### EduPortal API - Auth Controller
### Authentication and user management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5129/api/auth
@contentType = application/json

### ===========================================
### REGISTER - Create a new user
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Password123!",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "phoneNumber": "+905551234567"
}

### ===========================================
### LOGIN - User login
### ===========================================
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@eduportal.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### ===========================================
### CHANGE PASSWORD - Change user password (Requires Auth)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/change-password
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{
  "currentPassword": "OldPassword123!",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123!",
  "confirmNewPassword": "NewPassword123!"
}

### ===========================================
### GET CURRENT USER - Get authenticated user info (Requires Auth)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
